# ManageMeals API

Backend for [ManageMeals](https://managemeals.com) — recipe manager. Multi-service repo; each service runs in its own Docker container.

| Service | Directory | Role |
|---------|-----------|------|
| API | `src/` | Fastify HTTP API |
| Queue | `queue/` | RabbitMQ consumer (Node.js) |
| Scraper | `scraper/` | Python recipe URL scraper |
| Search sync | `search/` | MongoDB → Typesense sync |
| Webhooks | `webhooks/` | Cronjob for webhook data in DB |

**Stack:** Node.js ESM + TypeScript, Fastify v5, TypeBox, MongoDB, Redis, Typesense, RabbitMQ, S3, JWT/bcrypt/OAuth, GoCardless/PayPal, SMTP.

**Dev (API):** `npm run dev` (tsx watch) · `npm run build` · `npm start`

**Docker:** use `make` — `make up-infra` / `make stop-infra` / `make clean-infra`; `make up-app` / `make upd-app` / `make stop-app`; `make up-selfhost`. Local overrides: `*.override.yaml`.

**Config:** env vars via `src/plugins/env.ts` (`.env` in non-prod). Never commit secrets. New vars need both `envSchema` in `env.ts` and the `config` block in `custom-types.d.ts`.

**Docs:** `CLAUDE.md` and `README.md` for fuller reference.
